description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/24876/documentation

This dataset represents the production of one m3 of glued laminated timber. The input of wood is assumed to be kiln dried sawn softwood, more specifically spruce. A part of the dried softwood is already planed. The activity takes place at a glulam mill.;; The dataset is based on Canadian average but is representative of Quebec's production.

Activity starts at the entrance of the production site. it includes:
- the input materials and energy to the production processes received at the factory gate;
- the infrastructures (building, furnace for wood).

Activity ends at the gate of the production site. 
Outputs include:
- the material outputs (glued laminated timber and by-products);
- process emissions;
- combustion emissions from wood (internal use).
